Redshift (extra)
	•	Do we require private-only access via DX/VPN/PrivateLink?
	•	Enable Enhanced VPC Routing?
	•	WLM queues & concurrency targets?
	•	Snapshot copy: target region + KMS key?
	•	Data sharing between clusters/namespaces?

Athena (extra)
	•	Enforce workgroup-only usage?
	•	Preferred file format (Parquet/Iceberg)?
	•	Partition rules and who manages them?
	•	Per-workgroup query spend limit?

DataZone / Lake Formation
	•	Exact producer/consumer roles and approval workflow?
	•	LF permission model (db/table/column masking)?
	•	Metadata/glossary ownership?

Security/Compliance
	•	Tagging standard (Owner, CostCenter, DataClassification).
	•	PHI detection via Macie—scope & cadence?
	•	Log retention per type; S3 Object Lock compliance mode on audit buckets?
	•	Region allowlist via SCPs?

Networking
	•	Final subnet list (3 AZs), NAT strategy, DNS (Route 53).
	•	VPC endpoints list confirmation (S3, KMS, STS, Glue, SSM, CW, Secrets).
	•	Egress controls (no internet path?)—use centralized egress?

DR/Ops
	•	RTO/RPO targets; quarterly restore tests needed?
	•	Pager/Teams alerting for Admin/Break-glass role assumption?
	•	Monthly access review cadence?

Cost
	•	Non-prod scale smaller? Use Redshift Serverless for Dev/Test?
	•	Budgets & alerts by env.
